title: Kwe$t - New Line EP (2014) Electro/Hip-Hop/Dubstep
description:
Hey everyone thanks for stopping by, I really appreciate the time you have taken to find and download this, and most importantly I hope you enjoy it. I would like to go on about how many people have helped me so far along the way, and describe the long list of musical influences that enlighten and inspire me every day. I cannot possibly list it all without forgetting some, so you know who you are, and I thank you from the bottom of my heart.
